f3bf24daa9f8df5664a9ca14f319021403b","tid":323923,"uid":28834,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-16T09:10:43.000Z","msg":"呢d唔係抑鬱症<br />\n你走到出黎就無事架喇 唔好沉醉係舊時<br />\nmove on"},{"pid":"4e1e84b5a64aa731a6279a8bf689d696f92662ad","tid":323923,"uid":97136,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-16T09:16:16.000Z","msg":"試下做運動"},{"pid":"e29ef8ee1bdddb49d85ca528601e950beb5e369f","tid":323923,"uid":50114,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-16T09:21:47.000Z","msg":"我經歷過<br />\n如果你怕有抑鬱，你行出第一步！<br />\n嘗試同人傾多計，傾完咪喊！<br />\n<br />\n我之前想過死，所以我身邊有朋友做輔導，我主動搵佢傾計！好多人話時間幫到你，但坦言如果日日坐係度，時間係幫唔到你<br />\n<br />\n加油！"},{"pid":"07f355b7e6a30a7745e8eb5ff24c466334465297","tid":323923,"uid":47480,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-16T09:22:19.000Z","msg":"超出每小時發表主題數量上限，請稍候再試"},{"pid":"7c57a710be10437ee99e84855b81b7db0125b4e6","tid":323923,"uid":50114,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-16T09:25:09.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://m.youtube.com/watch?v=iOFI213MuKM\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fm.youtube.com%2Fwatch%3Fv%3DiOFI213MuKM&d=LQWQmKbjtdkBJpbj%2B%2FgmgKWGW%2FHqnCni%2B1xW1zXhD2s%3D&h=ddfcda79\" target=\"_blank\">https://m.youtube.com/watch?v=iOFI213MuKM</a><br />\n<br />\n另一個朋友分享比我，承認好多感覺係必經階段<br />\n即使我今日睇返，我都感受到當日嘅痛！"},{"pid":"57e0fa5d25a808a50ee30729126995635c88691b","tid":323923,"uid":36131,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-16T09:26:48.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote><blockquote><blockquote><blockquote>你要做嘅野就係充實自己嘅生活嚟忘記佢，唔係話因為忘記唔到而冇動力做野</blockquote><br />\n個問題係連充實自己嘅動力都無 咩都無興趣 不如你search下抑鬱係點先啦</blockquote><br />\n你缺乏嘅係一個藉口，畀一個藉口自己去做野，咁就得</blockquote><br />\n<a href=\"https://youtu.be/EJ_S5Rjt_iI\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fyoutu.be%2FEJ_S5Rjt_iI&d=LQWQmKbjtdkBJpbj%2B%2FgmgKWGW%2FHqnCni%2B1xW1zXhD2s%3D&h=974b7e99\" target=\"_blank\">https://youtu.be/EJ_S5Rjt_iI</a><br />\nWatch it seriously, you will know what I mean. Depression is when you don't have the motivation to do anything and even get out of the bed.</blockquote><br />\n我知你冇動力，搵個藉口畀自己，逼自己做野，明唔明？同frd出去做下運動行下山，明唔明？</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n已經好唔開心 好無心機<br />\n仲要逼自己做呢樣 做果樣<br />\n平時已經逼緊自己去番工<br />\n我已經覺得抖唔到氣"},{"pid":"7ce3a361574b58b1d6f6dc1957430c0c6e566315","tid":323923,"uid":36131,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-16T09:30:59.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>on9 仔 曬埋啲時間 又傷害自己身體<br />\n<br />\n過一排你唔好後悔 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/369.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n其實明知而家做嘅野浪費緊時間<br />\n但完全冇動力去改變<br />\n<br />\n以前我會諗好多方法或者捱夜去改善自己生活<br />\n但而家每晚我只想快啲入睡 咩都唔洗諗<br />\n最好唔好醒<br />\n<br />\n就算錯過一次又一次嘅機會<br />\n我都已經冇能力再去做啲咩<br />\n<br />\n而家係會諗人生好漫長<br />\n幾時先可以快快趣趣過完"},{"pid":"49b175a60c9dd9577c378bf7d30f6f3c6dac8929","tid":323923,"uid":124973,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-16T11:06:34.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><a href=\"https://m.youtube.com/watch?v=iOFI213MuKM\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fm.youtube.com%2Fwatch%3Fv%3DiOFI213MuKM&d=LQWQmKbjtdkBJpbj%2B%2FgmgKWGW%2FHqnCni%2B1xW1zXhD2s%3D&h=ddfcda79\" target=\"_blank\">https://m.youtube.com/watch?v=iOFI213MuKM</a><br />\n<br />\n另一個朋友分享比我，承認好多感覺係必經階段<br />\n即使我今日睇返，我都感受到當日嘅痛！</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n片段好好。。。正經歷緊rebuilding 的過程"},{"pid":"47439054552d9e38d03fafe505e19e758bf2067b","tid":323923,"uid":28834,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-16T11:25:03.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote><a href=\"https://m.youtube.com/watch?v=iOFI213MuKM\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fm.youtube.com%2Fwatch%3Fv%3DiOFI213MuKM&d=LQWQmKbjtdkBJpbj%2B%2FgmgKWGW%2FHqnCni%2B1xW1zXhD2s%3D&h=ddfcda79\" target=\"_blank\">https://m.youtube.com/watch?v=iOFI213MuKM</a><br />\n<br />\n另一個朋友分享比我，承認好多感覺係必經階段<br />\n即使我今日睇返，我都感受到當日嘅痛！</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n片段好好。。。正經歷緊rebuilding 的過程</blo